bo International Airport|Kalibo]], [[Kota Kinabalu International Airport|Kota Kinabalu]], [[Kuala Lumpur International Airport|Kuala Lumpur\u2013International]], [[Legazpi Airport|Legazpi]], [[Macau International Airport|Macau]], [[Melbourne Airport|Melbourne]], [[Chubu Centrair International Airport|Nagoya\u2013Centrair]], [[Kansai International Airport|Osaka\u2013Kansai]], [[Labo Airport|Ozamiz]], [[Pagadian Airport|Pagadian]], [[Puerto Princesa International Airport|Puerto Princesa]], [[Roxas Airport|Roxas]], [[San Jose Airport (Mindoro)|San Jose (Mindoro)]], [[Incheon International Airport|Seoul\u2013Incheon]], [[Shanghai Pudong International Airport|Shanghai\u2013Pudong]], [[Shenzhen Bao'an International Airport|Shenzhen]], [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]], [[Sydney Airport|Sydney]], [[Daniel Z. Romualdez Airport|Tacloban]], [[Bohol\u2013Panglao International Airport|Tagbilaran]], [[Taoyuan International Airport|Taipei\u2013Taoyuan]], [[Narita International Airport|Tokyo\u2013Narita]], [[Tuguegarao Airport|Tuguegarao]], [[Virac Airport|Virac]], [[Xiamen Gaoqi International Airport|Xiamen]], [[Zamboanga International Airport|Zamboanga]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Cebu Pacific]]<br/>{{nowrap|operated by [[Cebgo]]}}|[[Basco Airport|Basco]], [[Francisco B. Reyes Airport|Busuanga]], [[Godofredo P. Ramos Airport|Caticlan]], [[Mactan-Cebu International Airport|Cebu]], [[Kalibo International Airport|Kalibo]], [[Legazpi Airport|Legazpi]], [[Marinduque Airport|Marinduque]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Cebu Pacific to offer Manila-Marinduque route April 1 |url=http://www.pna.gov.ph/articles/1063844 |website=www.pna.gov.ph |language=en}}</ref> [[Moises R. Espinosa Airport|Masbate]], [[Naga Airport|Naga]], [[Sayak Airport|Siargao]], [[Tugdan Airport|Tablas]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[China Airlines]]|[[Kaohsiung International Airport|Kaohsiung]], [[Taoyuan International Airport|Taipei\u2013Taoyuan]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[China Eastern Airlines]]|[[Shanghai Pudong International Airport|Shanghai\u2013Pudong]